### Park Adventure - Authentication API Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

###
### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/health
Accept: application/json

###
### 2. Đăng ký tài khoản mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "0987654321",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "email": "nguyenvana@example.com",
  "dateOfBirth": "1995-05-15",
  "gender": "MALE"
}

###
### 3. Đăng ký với mã giới thiệu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "0912345678",
  "password": "password456",
  "fullName": "Trần Thị B",
  "email": "tranthib@example.com",
  "referralCode": "ABC12345"
}

###
### 4. Đăng nhập
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "0987654321",
  "password": "password123"
}

###
### 5. Test với số điện thoại không hợp lệ
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "123",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Test User"
}

###
### 6. Test với password ngắn
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "0901234567",
  "password": "123",
  "fullName": "Test User"
}

###
### 7. Test đăng nhập với sai mật khẩu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "0987654321",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###
### 8. Test JWT Authentication - Lấy thông tin user
### Lưu ý: Thay YOUR_JWT_TOKEN bằng token nhận được từ login/register
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 9. Test JWT Authentication - Simple test
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/test-auth
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 10. Test protected route không có token (Expected: 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Accept: application/json

### =====================================================
### GAME ENDPOINTS
### =====================================================

###
### 11. Lấy danh sách game (public - không cần token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

###
### 12. Lấy danh sách game theo category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games?category=Adventure&page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

###
### 13. Tìm kiếm game
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games?search=tàu lượn&page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

###
### 14. Lấy danh sách game nổi bật
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/featured?limit=5
Accept: application/json

###
### 15. Lấy danh sách categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/categories
Accept: application/json

###
### 16. Lấy chi tiết một game
### Thay GAME_ID bằng ID thực tế
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/GAME_ID
Accept: application/json

###
### 17. Tạo game mới (Admin only - cần JWT token có role ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tàu lượn siêu tốc",
  "description": "Trò chơi tàu lượn siêu tốc với tốc độ lên đến 80km/h, mang đến trải nghiệm phiêu lưu mạo hiểm đầy thú vị.",
  "shortDescription": "Tàu lượn tốc độ cao, trải nghiệm mạo hiểm",
  "category": "Adventure",
  "pricePerTurn": "50000",
  "durationMinutes": 5,
  "location": "Khu A - Phiêu lưu",
  "thumbnailUrl": "https://example.com/roller-coaster.jpg",
  "galleryUrls": ["https://example.com/rc1.jpg", "https://example.com/rc2.jpg"],
  "ageRequired": 12,
  "heightRequired": 140,
  "maxCapacity": 24,
  "riskLevel": 4,
  "isFeatured": true
}

###
### 18. Cập nhật game (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/games/GAME_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pricePerTurn": "55000",
  "isFeatured": true,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###
### 19. Xóa game (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/games/GAME_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 20. Test tạo game không có quyền Admin (Expected: 403)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Game",
  "pricePerTurn": "10000"
}

###
### 21. Test tạo game không có token (Expected: 401)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Game",
  "pricePerTurn": "10000"
}

### =====================================================
### CARD ENDPOINTS
### =====================================================

###
### 22. Danh sách thẻ của tôi
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cards
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 23. Liên kết thẻ vật lý
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cards/link
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "physicalCardUid": "04A3B2C1D5E6F7",
  "cardName": "Thẻ chính",
  "pin": "1234"
}

###
### 24. Cập nhật thẻ
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/cards/CARD_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardName": "Thẻ VIP"
}

###
### 25. Khóa thẻ
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cards/CARD_ID/block
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Mất thẻ"
}

###
### 26. Mở khóa thẻ
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cards/CARD_ID/unblock
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 27. Hủy liên kết thẻ
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/cards/CARD_ID/unlink
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

### =====================================================
### VOUCHER ENDPOINTS
### =====================================================

###
### 28. Danh sách voucher đang có (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

###
### 29. Tìm voucher theo mã
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers/code/SUMMER2024
Accept: application/json

###
### 30. Nhận voucher vào ví
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers/VOUCHER_ID/claim
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 31. Voucher của tôi
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers/my-vouchers?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 32. Tạo voucher (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SUMMER2024",
  "title": "Giảm 20% mùa hè",
  "description": "Giảm 20% cho tất cả trò chơi trong tháng 6-8",
  "discountType": "PERCENT",
  "discountValue": "20",
  "maxDiscount": "100000",
  "minOrderValue": "50000",
  "usageLimit": 1000,
  "perUserLimit": 1,
  "startDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-08-31T23:59:59Z"
}

###
### 33. Cập nhật voucher (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers/VOUCHER_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###
### 34. Xóa voucher (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers/VOUCHER_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

### =====================================================
### ORDER ENDPOINTS (Đặt vé)
### =====================================================

###
### 35. Tạo đơn hàng (mua vé bằng số dư ví)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "gameId": "GAME_ID_1", "quantity": 2 },
    { "gameId": "GAME_ID_2", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "paymentMethod": "BALANCE",
  "note": "Mua vé cho gia đình"
}

###
### 36. Tạo đơn hàng có voucher
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "gameId": "GAME_ID_1", "quantity": 3 }
  ],
  "voucherCode": "SUMMER2024",
  "paymentMethod": "BALANCE"
}

###
### 37. Lịch sử đơn hàng
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 38. Chi tiết đơn hàng
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/ORDER_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 39. Hủy đơn hàng
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/ORDER_ID/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Đổi ý không muốn chơi"
}

###
### 40. Danh sách vé của tôi
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

### =====================================================
### WALLET ENDPOINTS (Ví tiền)
### =====================================================

###
### 41. Xem số dư ví
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 42. Nạp tiền
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wallet/topup
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": "200000",
  "method": "MOMO"
}

###
### 43. Lịch sử giao dịch (tất cả)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallet/transactions?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 44. Lịch sử giao dịch (theo loại)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallet/transactions?type=TOPUP&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
### 45. Lịch sử thanh toán
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallet/payments?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

### =====================================================
### GAME REVIEW ENDPOINTS
### =====================================================

###
### 46. Xem đánh giá của game (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/GAME_ID/reviews?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

###
### 47. Viết đánh giá
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reviews
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "GAME_ID",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Trò chơi rất thú vị, cả gia đình đều thích!"
}

###
### 48. Sửa đánh giá
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/reviews/REVIEW_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Vui nhưng hơi ngắn"
}

###
### 49. Xóa đánh giá
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/reviews/REVIEW_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

